skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: get me up
des:
Note: *Make sure the skill is enabled before trying to say "Get Me Up"

This is the perfect app for people who are being a bit lazy but need to get up and be productive.

Tell Alexa to 'get me up' and she will try her best to help you be productive. 

If she wasn't convincing enough, you can tell her 'no' or 'I don't feel like it' and she will keep trying to help you get up.

Say 'Okay' or one of the Alexa stop words to stop the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
